articles.description: Regional parts of New South Wales, Queensland and Victoria have been hit with debilitating mice infestations which are destroying crops, houses and the livelihoods of many.
articles.content:
Farmers left at breaking point by the endless plagues of mice ravaging their properties fear they face a second wave of the pests on the other side of winter.
